graph TD
    CLI[cmd_webdriver.cpp CLI entry] --> SRV[webdriver_server.cpp HTTP server]
    SRV -->|register routes| ROUTES[route handlers per endpoint]
    SRV -->|owns| SESSMAP[sessions HashMap]
    ROUTES --> SESS[webdriver_session.cpp]
    ROUTES --> LOC[webdriver_locator.cpp]
    ROUTES --> ACT[webdriver_actions.cpp]
    ROUTES --> ERR[webdriver_errors.cpp]

    SESS -->|owns per session| UICON[headless UiContext]
    SESS -->|owns| REG[ElementRegistry UUID to View]
    SESS -->|load and layout| PIPE[load_html_doc then layout_html_doc]

    LOC -->|CSS| MATCH[selector_matcher_matches]
    LOC -->|walk| VTREE[layout View tree]

    ACT -->|synthesize| RDT[RdtEvent]
    RDT --> HE[handle_event GUI input path]

    ERR -->|name and status| WIRE[W3C error JSON]
